{"tid":2379501,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政府決定用中醫醫武漢肺炎！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2021-01-25T09:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T19:56:39.000Z","uid":34714,"like":17,"dislike":110,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"29efd0177443af3ff5b6ef60152e80b45818b05b","tid":2379501,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6297a59b3144ceb85f466ca4a12d55a56f6369c","tid":2379501,"uid":49577,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:22:41.000Z","msg":"汁?"},{"pid":"36f8815964ec6e4dcb6df560ee289349a25a8230","tid":2379501,"uid":325346,"like":30,"dislike":7,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"f6297a59b3144ceb85f466ca4a12d55a56f6369c","tid":2379501,"uid":49577,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:22:41.000Z","msg":"汁?"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:23:53.000Z","msg":"輔助啫<br />\n唔係個個都用中藥<br />\n只用在輕症病人"},{"pid":"1559a67a998c9863ca07a87dba385aa172d66af4","tid":2379501,"uid":281492,"like":5,"dislike":16,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"f6297a59b3144ceb85f466ca4a12d55a56f6369c","tid":2379501,"uid":49577,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:22:41.000Z","msg":"汁?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:24:10.000Z","msg":"經濟日報唔貼link<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【中醫治療】醫管局為亞博新冠肺炎患者提供中醫治療　中醫：可快速紓緩徵狀<br />\n<br />\n16:49 2021/01/25<br />\n<br />\n本地新冠肺炎疫情反覆，今日（25日）新增73宗確診個案，包括4宗輸入個案、69宗本地個案，37男36女，年齡介乎1個月至 歲，其中有38宗涉源頭不明感染，累計共10,159宗病例。本地個案有14宗於油尖旺區內檢出，包括13宗於強制檢測區內，1宗在檢測區外。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局總行政經理（中醫）黃巧雲表示，去年4月開始醫管局推行中醫門診特別診療服務，為在公立醫院康復出院的新冠肺炎病人提供免費中醫門診服務，參與人數至今已逾700名。<br />\n<br />\n而由明天１月２６日開始，在亞博社區治療設施中提供中醫治療服務，服務免費屬自願性質，希望可以紓緩徵狀，需要由中醫及西醫評估，是否接受中醫服務。醫管局已成立小組，包括３間大學的中醫臨床及中醫專家，西醫方面包括傳染病學及毒理學專家。狷病人接受首次診療後，會安排病人複診及治療，出院後仍可以接受中醫治療。<br />\n<br />\n香港中文大學中醫學院副院長林志秀指出，中醫藥成為新冠肺炎治療很重要部分，內地經驗有效率逾九成以上，快速緩解臨床症狀，可以提升治癮率以及減少輕症出現併發症。至於中醫中藥處方，內地臨床經驗，清肺排毒湯有效果。"},{"pid":"244610ff2afe479555f9e197f6582f5235952c77","tid":2379501,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"f6297a59b3144ceb85f466ca4a12d55a56f6369c","tid":2379501,"uid":49577,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:22:41.000Z","msg":"汁?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:24:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2379501\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2379501</a>"},{"pid":"d860ca218f82fd80399eae2b8bd61042b66775f4","tid":2379501,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36f8815964ec6e4dcb6df560ee289349a25a8230","tid":2379501,"uid":325346,"like":30,"dislike":7,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"f6297a59b3144ceb85f466ca4a12d55a56f6369c","tid":2379501,"uid":49577,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:22:41.000Z","msg":"汁?"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:23:53.000Z","msg":"輔助啫<br />\n唔係個個都用中藥<br />\n只用在輕症病人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:24:25.000Z","msg":"嗯嗯<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6efbb2c63b15bd92c4b5fb64487cfa986fcb1ae0","tid":2379501,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:25:18.000Z","msg":"中醫羊"},{"pid":"1730be69b8f0ed8efab67837b74a98134859f596","tid":2379501,"uid":78515,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:25:53.000Z","msg":"簡稱 武漢茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39786c6be2adeb19bddeb654932104d53b88e518","tid":2379501,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:26:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"099a93d531f70e1b403b792987c254419c6d8bbe","tid"